  "description": "Maximum density (120 grains/sec) with 12ms Rectangular window grains — at 12 voices, 1440 grain events per second total. The ear resolves this as continuous noise-like texture with spectral coloration from the underlying Pulse oscillator (source=2). Position scatter=0.9 with a fast-wandering position (LFO→position at 0.25Hz). Every moment the granulator is reading from a different part of the buffer. The Pulse wave's harmonic series becomes a storm of spectral fragments.",
